room_title: Escape room "Murder Mystery Masquerade" by Padlock Escape Games in College Station
review: The best part of this escape room is that many people can be involved at a time.  They have lots of concurrent puzzles for this reason.  However, some puzzles were executed so that (as they stated) you had to ask for clues.  I personally prefer their other two rooms because they make more sense.  However, I did escape and enjoy the hour.
